English: Waiting for host to return you to lobby...
Description: A text that is shown for clients in the expedition failed/success screen, to indicate that it is up to the host to return the group to the lobby.

French.Translation: En attente de l'hôte pour retourner au salon...

Italian.Translation: In attesa che l'host ti riporti alla lobby...

German.Translation: Auf den Host warten, der Sie in die Lobby zurückbringt ...

Spanish.Translation: Esperando a que el anfitrión vuelva a la sala...

Russian.Translation: Ожидайте, пока организатор вернет вас в лобби...

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Aguardando o anfitrião devolver você ao lobby...

Polish.Translation: Oczekiwanie na przeniesienie do lobby przez hosta...

Japanese.Translation: ホストがあなたをロビーに戻すのを待っています...

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 等待主機將你送回大廳……

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 正在等待厅主送回大厅……

name: ExpeditionSuccessPage.WaitingForHostButton
